{"tid":1854064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【封關救港】醫管局員工陣線：逾6500醫護確認參與下周一罷工","createTime":"2020-01-31T09:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T14:39:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"afd99eac12b8bb68f568ec4dd21cb886237d3920","tid":1854064,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1505880_1_L_20200131171729.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1505880_1_L_20200131171729.jpg&h=bdfcf8cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505880-20200131.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505880-20200131.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=de34d838\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505880-20200131.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=166d6802\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505880-20200131.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n本港武漢肺炎確診數字上升，令前線醫護壓力大增。醫管局員工陣線表示，目前已收到超過6500人確認會參與下星期一的罷工活動，當中逾7成為護士，8%為醫生。工會亦將於明日舉行特別會員大會，投票決定是否展開罷工行動。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明表示，目前只實施部分封關和依賴自我申報系統，並不足以堵截源頭，強調當前只有封關才能避免社區出現大規模感染。工會早於上周已向醫管局提出多項訴求，但對方至今仍然未有回應，雙方將於2月2日會面。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線副主席羅卓堯指，罷工行動將分兩階段進行。若醫管局在首日仍然未能回應訴求，不排除會呼籲所有會員參加罷工，屆時或可能影響緊急服務。他強調，工會原意並不想罷工，但如果政府仍然漠視訴求，不排除會有進一步行動。"},{"pid":"79eedd4bdf719e9e0ef85aeba31c2a067dc53cdd","tid":1854064,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"f9b1b963dc3e20e964b5c144127d4837e8ad39b2","tid":1854064,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xk8WqoZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxk8WqoZ.jpg&h=78a5bbd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇傳媒及出版嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n組織工會 全面罷工</span></span><br />\n【港人自救，全民防疫】行動<br />\n - 問卷 - <a href=\"https://forms.gle/8LUQLEv94tbhxfxe9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F8LUQLEv94tbhxfxe9&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=3aeb52be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/8LUQLEv94tbhxfxe9</a><br />\n<br />\n- - -<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［港共不封關，全港冚家剷］香港傳媒及出版職工會-籌組中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847821\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n又一個工會準備誕生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路過入黎幫手推個post  謝謝<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"6622c6655ed03841d48d293522c2776de7116e69","tid":1854064,"uid":288175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405a53152f88d9dcce4de582bafb0625d35b4dc8","tid":1854064,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"多D多D"},{"pid":"dc369dbeadd056fe3837f865450142c25f59a1de","tid":1854064,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:02:19.000Z","msg":"星期六同星期日個談判都唔會傾到咩返黎"},{"pid":"7d9c53b94e48e409e4b156a005e1c09b57cea7f2","tid":1854064,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc369dbeadd056fe3837f865450142c25f59a1de","tid":1854064,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:02:19.000Z","msg":"星期六同星期日個談判都唔會傾到咩返黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"傾到都未用<br />\n唔覺得依家做咩都太遲咩"},{"pid":"1a510edd099c7475d3e115c3e